## B. Partial — harus dilengkapi (prioritas tinggi)

### B1 · Master API live ERP (P0-1) — BLOCKER go-live

| | |
|---|---|
| **Posisi** | Master Data modal · picker material (Struktur, Material) |
| **SEBELUM** | Adapter `masterApiAdapter.js` sync ke cache; UI tetap baca seed IndexedDB; flag API via `window.__BOM_*__` |
| **SESUDAH** | Mode `MASTER_SOURCE=api` → picker non-kayu 100% dari ERP; seed hanya fallback dev |
| **Acceptance** | 1. Set `window.__BOM_MASTER_SOURCE__='api'` + `__BOM_API_BASE__` → picker hardware/upholstery G632L tampil SKU ERP<br>2. Harga satuan = API (bukan seed ZAN stale)<br>3. Mode `seed` (default) → `npm test` tetap green tanpa API<br>4. Gagal API → fallback seed + banner warning (tidak crash)<br>5. Mapping field ERP → shape `resolveMaterial()` terdokumentasi 1 halaman |
| **File** | `src/services/masterApiAdapter.js`, `src/services/masterStorage.js`, `src/components/fields/MasterCombos.jsx`, `SearchableSelect.jsx` |
| **Owner** | BE (endpoint) + FE (wire picker + error state) |

### B2 · Persist project ke ERP (P0-4) — BLOCKER multi-user

| | |
|---|---|
| **Posisi** | Auto-save editor · Dashboard CRUD |
| **SEBELUM** | `projectApiAdapter.js` debounce PATCH; IndexedDB = source of truth; conflict hanya throw console |
| **SESUDAH** | Draft/submitted/approved di ERP; IDB = cache offline |
| **Acceptance** | 1. Mode `PROJECT_SOURCE=api` → save editor → PATCH `/v1/projects/{id}` ≤ 3 detik setelah edit<br>2. Status: `draft` default, bisa set `submitted`<br>3. Conflict 409 → toast user: "BOM diubah user lain"<br>4. 2 browser/tab: edit bersamaan → tidak silent overwrite<br>5. Mode `local` → perilaku sekarang unchanged |
| **File** | `src/services/projectApiAdapter.js`, `src/services/projectStorage.js`, `src/pages/BOMEditor.jsx` |
| **Kontrak** | [API-Contract-BOM-Platform.mmd](../API-Contract-BOM-Platform.mmd) § Projects |

### B3 · Product picker ERP (P1-6)

| | |
|---|---|
| **Posisi** | Product Panel — Kode/Nama BOM |
| **SEBELUM** | Input teks bebas |
| **SESUDAH** | SearchableSelect dari `/manufacture/products` atau API contract |
| **Acceptance** | 1. Pilih produk ERP → auto-fill: kode, nama, customer, itemType, dimensi (jika ada)<br>2. Manual override nama tetap boleh<br>3. Offline/seed mode → free text seperti sekarang<br>4. UAT: buat project G632L dari wizard + pilih produk ERP → header terisi konsisten |

